{"TopicId":122175,"ForumId":34,"TopicTitle":"[1.0.5 ] KSC Floodlight (24.02.2016)","CreatedByName":"Divico","CreatedById":119955,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-02T20:28:52Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Divico","CreatedById":119955,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-02T20:28:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:18px;\u0022\u003EKSC Floodlight\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdds 4 Floodlight Towers to the KSC Launchpad.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nClick the towers to turn on the light.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ciframe class=\u0022imgur-album\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022550\u0022 src=\u0022//imgur.com/a/Boekq/embed?background=ffffff\u0026amp;text=1a1a1a\u0026amp;link=4e76c9\u0022 width=\u0022100%\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://spacedock.info/mod/264/KSC%20Floodlight\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022OwaNQsx.png\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/OwaNQsx.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRequires \u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalstuff.com/mod/165/Kerbal%20Konstructs\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EKerbalKonstructs\u003C/a\u003E (included).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ELicense\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ecc-by-nc-sa-4.0\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-02-24T11:59:28Z\u0022 title=\u002202/24/2016 11:59  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 24, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Divico\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EUpload to SpaceDock\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"rabidninjawombat","CreatedById":108889,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-02T20:31:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ELove it! Definitely adding to my install\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"monstah","CreatedById":95210,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-02T20:49:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ENice!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bev7787","CreatedById":136501,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-02T21:35:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Ebeautiful\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MK3424","CreatedById":19932,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-02T23:16:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ENice little addition to make the launchpad a bit beter looking, especially at night.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AlphaAsh","CreatedById":105348,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-03T09:30:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EExcellent. 10/10 would illuminate launchpad again.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Divico","CreatedById":119955,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-03T11:56:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThanks for the comments! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E(\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/threads/44437-KSC-Needs-Pad-Lighting!\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EIt was about time, someone made this mod...\u003C/a\u003E)\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pizzaoverhead","CreatedById":26349,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-03T20:18:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EBeautiful! KSC has been missing lightning towers for far too long! They\u0027re a very distinctive part of most launch sites.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://www.learnwithmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/2014-1152-s-Atlas_5_launch_pad.jpg\u0022 alt=\u00222014-1152-s-Atlas_5_launch_pad.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"skykooler","CreatedById":60459,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-04T05:20:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ELooks cool! They do kind of dwarf most KSP rockets, though.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Divico","CreatedById":119955,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-04T09:27:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022skykooler\u0022 data-cite=\u0022skykooler\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ELooks cool! They do kind of dwarf most KSP rockets, though.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EYou are kind of right...\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI tried to use real-ish numbers. These towers seem to be in the range of 150m - 180m. The NASA VAB is 160m. So I scaled it to that.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027ll test what a 0.75 or even 0.5 scale looks like.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NecroBones","CreatedById":105424,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-08T14:13:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI just spotted this on KerbalStuff. Woohoo! It\u0027s something I\u0027ve been meaning to make, if no one else did. I just haven\u0027t had the time to look into Kerbal Konstructs, etc.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027m going to download this right away!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nhawks17","CreatedById":32999,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-08T23:43:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EFor anyone interested I changed the textures for these to make them feel more stock-alike. Its just changing the red to a darker grey. I prefer it more than the red but I\u0027m in love with this mod \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\u003Cp\u003E[highlight]\u003C/p\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www./download/767tbua9cxn7tjp/KSC_Floodlight_AltTextures.zip\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EDownload Here\u003C/a\u003E[/highlight]\u003Cblockquote lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022//imgur.com/a/ZOUsl\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EJavascript is disabled. View full album\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NecroBones","CreatedById":105424,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-09T13:36:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Divico\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Divico\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EYou are kind of right...\u003Cp\u003EI tried to use real-ish numbers. These towers seem to be in the range of 150m - 180m. The NASA VAB is 160m. So I scaled it to that.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027ll test what a 0.75 or even 0.5 scale looks like.\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESince the real-life towers are lightning rods, generally they need to be a bit taller than the tallest rockets that will be on the pad. So making them as tall as the VAB is probably reasonable.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nhawks17","CreatedById":32999,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-09T15:14:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI dunno if this would be possible as I don\u0027t know how Kerbal Konstructs works but could the lights rotate up and down to adjust where the light is pointing at depending on your ship?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Divico","CreatedById":119955,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-13T20:49:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nhawks17\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Nhawks17\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EI dunno if this would be possible as I don\u0027t know how Kerbal Konstructs works but could the lights rotate up and down to adjust where the light is pointing at depending on your ship?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThat\u0027s not possible. KK can only run an animation (i.e. light) on mouse click and run it backwards on the second click.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nhawks17","CreatedById":32999,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-13T21:16:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Divico\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Divico\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EThat\u0027s not possible. KK can only run an animation (i.e. light) on mouse click and run it backwards on the second click.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAh ok, just thought I\u0027d ask \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dman Revolution","CreatedById":118094,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-11-08T18:44:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ECould you make them hollow and have a ladder on the side so you can go up them?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AlmostNASA","CreatedById":158711,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-15T23:22:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow I feel sad because KerbalStuff has closed and CKAN uses it so now I can\u0027t get this.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Abhishek Adhikari","CreatedById":154450,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-20T06:26:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlease somebody zip the lightning tower addon and share somewhere because kerbalstuff is closed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jansn67","CreatedById":158367,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-20T10:24:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHave the original released zip in my archive. Wait a week if it appears on Spacedock,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nif not, then i could upload it.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFunny, just yesterday i grabbed it out to install ;-)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Abhishek Adhikari","CreatedById":154450,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-20T11:52:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJansn67,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlease!PLease!Please! email me the archieve at \u003Ca href=\u0022/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection\u0022 class=\u0022__cf_email__\u0022 data-cfemail=\u00226c0d0e04050d15191f045e5f2c0b010d0500420f0301\u0022\u003E[email\u0026#160;protected]\u003C/a\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlease I can\u0027t wait for that wonderful mod.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks in advance.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-20T17:24:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDivico hasnt been gone from the forums THAT long...\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nI\u0027d wait to see if \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/119955-divico/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022119955\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/119955-divico/\u0022\u003E@Divico\u003C/a\u003E comes back, and rehosts on SpaceDock.info himself...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Divico","CreatedById":119955,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-24T11:51:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUploaded to \u003Ca href=\u0022http://spacedock.info/mod/264/KSC%20Floodlight\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ESpaceDock \u003C/a\u003Ewith new KerbalKonstructs, works now in 1.0.5. Enjoy!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Courn Wallace","CreatedById":148753,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-24T18:21:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs it compatible with rescale mods? I\u0027ve installed but it is not showing up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Divico","CreatedById":119955,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-02-24T19:54:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222427800\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022122175\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221456338068\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022148753\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Courn Wallace\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Courn Wallace said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs it compatible with rescale mods? I\u0027ve installed but it is not showing up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI didn\u0027t test it. Depends on whether the current KerbalKonstructs version works with RSS or not (the last version did). The towers are most likely below surface. You\u0027ll have to raise the altitude manually; launch a ship and open the KK editor with Ctrl-K.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}